   <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">Never throw or drop material from a roof.  Always use chutes or containers to lower them.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">No work is permitted on roofs in the event of snow, wind, rain, lightning or storms. Should lightning be detected within a 10-mile radius, work will not resume for 30 minutes past the last lightning strike. </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Never go outside of the protected area.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Do not walk on a fragile roof.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Never stand on or lean through a guardrail system.</li>
      </ol>
   </conbody>
